Wieman has over 39 years of business experience with the firm and began his public accounting career with the Chicago office of Grant Thornton as a staff accountant in 1973 and was admitted to the partnership in 1986. He has served in a variety of other roles with the firm as the Audit Practice Leader in Chicago, Managing Partner of the Detroit office, the Managing Partner of the Midwest Region and Managing Partner of Audit and Advisory Services. In addition, Russ was elected to the Firm's Executive Committee and served as its Chairman for two years.  In 2010, he was appointed the Chief Financial Officer of the Firm., 9615='9:00-9:15 am}
